# Mega Marketing — client slug registry
# One slug per line. Used by encrypt.sh + get-password.sh to derive per-client
# passwords from filenames matching the pattern: YYYY-MM-<slug>-<type>.html
#
# Add a new line for every new client. Slug = kebab-case folder name minus the
# "client-" prefix. Order doesn't matter; the scripts sort by length descending
# so longer slugs (e.g. selective-support) match before shorter ones (support).
#
# Comments start with # and are ignored.

amal-umrah
darrusallam
eih-care
evaguard
halal-food-melbourne
hash-home-care
